---
import Base from "@layouts/Base.astro";
import Header from "@components/Header.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Base
  title="Now — What Berk is Working On (Updated) | Saralogy"
  description="What Berk is working on right now. Updated regularly."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">

    <section class="pt-16 pb-10 border-b border-gray-100">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Now</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Updated June 2026</p>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
        What I'm working on right now. A snapshot of current focus and priority.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="py-12 space-y-12">

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Work</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Actively searching for a Senior Marketing Manager role in Hamburg or DACH (target: August 2026). Looking for companies building something serious — ideally where I can own a full marketing function and bring AI-native thinking to the team.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          In the meantime, developing the vision-intelligence MVP (AI marketing platform for DACH SMEs). Currently in closed beta with 3 pilot customers. Targeting public beta launch by August 2026.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Music</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Working on a 4-track EP exploring the theme of "building." Recordings are 60% complete. Production is deliberate — not rushing to release; focusing on depth of process over volume.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Three tracks are already public: "Urban Wandering" (released), "Hamburg Nocturne" (released), and "Prototype" (demo). New track in progress.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Learning</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Deep dive into agentic AI architecture and retrieval-augmented generation (RAG). Building vision-intelligence has been my primary education here — seeing firsthand how AI-native systems differ from "AI-bolted-on" tools.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Life</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Moving into a new apartment in Hamburg. Wedding scheduled for September 12, 2026 (7 weeks away).
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          The big focus: building the compound revenue foundation I need to make the next decade work — salary + product + consulting. Getting the pieces in motion so the financial pressure is off and I can think clearly.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-100">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          <strong>Why this page?</strong> I keep this updated so people who know me (or are considering working with me) can see where I'm actually focused. It's more honest than a static bio.
        </p>
      </div>

    </section>

  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-gray-100 mt-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-8 flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-gray-500">
      <span>© 2026 Berk Saraloglu</span>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a href="/now" class="hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">Now</a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/berksaraloglu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/berksaraloglu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Base>
